reviews.text: The Lunchtime all you can eat Japanese shabu shabu hotpot is excellent for the price. Good quality vegetables and free flow curry. What more could a man want?

All you can eat shabu2, very delicious. Don’t take rice or you will be full haha. What I love is the ayce haagen daz ice cream, try to take before you eat because you have to queue for a little while. The queue for dinner is very long, be patient especially when you go in large group.
Awesome Japanese cuisine!!
Reasonably priced hot pot. Great for lunch
Average. Food service is slow. Nothing special about it.

reviews.text: The Lunchtime all you can eat Japanese shabu shabu hotpot is excellent for the price. Good quality vegetables and free flow curry. What more could a man want?
침사추이 점 보다 사람도 없고 더 깔끔하네요. 강추입니다. 저는 앞으로 침추 보다 코베 지점을 자주 갈 것 같아요.
침사추이점 보다 한가하고 좋았어요.먹방 아이들과 함께하면 최고~

叫左日本和牛同黑豚肉套餐，啲牛好肥美又嫩滑，每人三百幾，仲送蠔，帶子，魷魚添！另外菜任食，同埋有丸，雪糕，野飲！
服務唔錯，野食黎得快，收野都快手添
再加上用埋food gulu拎飛，人未到先拎飛，咁就唔駛等好耐嘞！
平民價格的牛鍋放題！
